asted vegetables, ramen, chicken, lamb and pork.","Marinate pork cutlets in shichimi togarashi, honey and yuzu juice. Grill them and serve with extra togarashi.","Shichimi togarashi keeps for months in a sealable jar or container stored in a cool, dark place."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","6 portions"]}